# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:11
translate chinese adrian13_156a2700:

    # "My phone starts buzzing in my pocket. I pull it out and see that Adrian is calling."
    "口袋里的手机开始震动。我掏出来一看，是艾德里安打来的。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:15
translate chinese adrian13_bea5e8cb:

    # pc "Hello?"
    pc "喂？"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:16
translate chinese adrian13_f9cf1bde:

    # gg "Hey, [pcname]. You busy?"
    gg "嘿，[pcname]。你忙吗？"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:17
translate chinese adrian13_e74e5c12:

    # pc "Not really. What's up?"
    pc "不忙。有什么事吗？"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:19
translate chinese adrian13_a2d441d4:

    # gg "There's this old arcade over on the east side of town that I haven't been to in years. I was wondering if you wanted to go check it out with me?"
    gg "城东那边有一家老街机厅，我好多年没去了。想问问你愿不愿意跟我一起去看看？"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:20
translate chinese adrian13_9ee91606:

    # pc "I didn't even know we had an arcade in town."
    pc "我甚至都不知道城里还有街机厅。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:22
translate chinese adrian13_6580f309:

    # gg "Yeah, I think most people have forgotten about it. I don't know how they stay in business."
    gg "是啊，我觉得大多数人都把它忘了。真不知道他们是怎么撑下来的。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:23
translate chinese adrian13_7860a0fb:

    # gg "But I kind of wanted to go check it out, just to see what they're doing there, and maybe get some ideas for my arcade."
    gg "但我挺想去看看的，就为了看看他们在那儿搞什么，说不定能给我自己的游戏厅找点灵感。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:27
translate chinese adrian13_34b5448b:

    # gg "Poggers! Come and get me?"
    gg "《Poggers》！来接我吗？"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:28
translate chinese adrian13_4724ea78:

    # pc "Sure, I'll be there in a few minutes."
    pc "行，我几分钟就到。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:29
translate chinese adrian13_5b5160ba:

    # gg "Okay, see you then!"
    gg "好的，到时候见！"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:33
translate chinese adrian13_75da4880:

    # gg "Aw, alright."
    gg "哎，行吧。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:35
translate chinese adrian13_c01438a1:

    # gg "Well, if you want to go sometime, just give me a call."
    gg "嗯，如果你哪天想去，就给我打电话。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:36
translate chinese adrian13_ba01fe47:

    # pc "Okay, see you later, Adrian."
    pc "好的，待会儿见，艾德里安。"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:37
translate chinese adrian13_225cc39e:

    # gg "See ya."
    gg "见。"

translate chinese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:2
    old "After Adrian has shown you her business plan,"
    new "在艾德里安向你展示完她的商业计划后，"

    # game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:3
    old "she will call you in the afternoon on the weekend and invite you out to an arcade with her."
    new "她会在周末的下午给你打电话，邀请你和她一起去游戏厅。"

    # game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:25
    old "Cool! Yeah, let's go"
    new "太棒了！好，我们去吧"

    # game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:31
    old "Not right now"
    new "现在不行"

